<h2>Find your Perfect 2020 Italy Summer Holiday.</h2>
<p> </p>
<p>We have over 85 years’ experience welcoming travellers to Europe’s most idyllic destinations.  </p>
<p>There are some fantastic special offers available when you book early, such as:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Save £85* per couple</strong> to coincide with our 85th birthday, when you book before 30 September 2019.</li>
<li><strong>£85** per person low deposit</strong> when you book before 30th September 2019.</li>
<li><strong>Early booking offers</strong><strong>:</strong> Our partner hotels reward early bookers with monetary discounts, which can be quite considerable. Visit our <a data-udi="umb://document/991245ba65ff4b36a0ec3d208715ed80" href="/{localLink:umb://document/991245ba65ff4b36a0ec3d208715ed80}" title="Destinations">destination pages</a> for details.</li>
<li><strong>Free*** walking maps:</strong> Book by 30 September 2019 and receive a free walking map, to selected destinations.</li>
<li><strong>Inghams Plus Offers:</strong> Great added value from our partner hotels such as <strong>Free</strong> packed lunches,<span> </span><strong>Free</strong> bike hire, <strong>Free </strong>guided walks and so much more.</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p>Look out for Summer Moments our new style magazine, bringing you inspiration for your next adventure with Inghams.</p>
<p> </p>
