</div>
<p> </p>
<p style="text-align: left;">*This offer applies to all summer 2020 holidays with a minimum of 7 nights duration. </p>
<p style="text-align: left;">**The remainder of the deposit (£65) will be due early October when our Main Edition brochure goes on sale.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">*** Maps will be posted from April 2020. Please note: these are good quality local walking maps, not 'walking guides' and may not include descriptions of walks in English. One map will be provided per booking for each stay of 7 nights or more.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Free map resorts: </strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Merano, Selva</p>
